[[File:Palais_présidentiel_à_Dakar_-_2.JPG|thumb]]
'''塞內加爾總統'''('''President of Senegal''')是[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]的[[國家元首|國家元首]]。根据2001年制定的[[宪法|宪法]]，将总统任期7年一任改为5年。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/world_now/2012/03/senegals-president-concedes-defeat-a-spot-of-rare-good-news-for-african-democracy.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-01-02 |archive-date=2018-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206001846/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/world_now/2012/03/senegals-president-concedes-defeat-a-spot-of-rare-good-news-for-african-democracy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

